room_title: Escape room "Off The Chain" by Escape Cape in Cape Girardeau
room_description:
You have 60 minutes to locate the clues and solve the puzzles to find what you need to stop your time and escape. All of the keys that you need are there ... but chained to the wall.

Each successful step you take in this room will get your chain just a little closer to the final box that holds the key to your great escape. This room is truly "OFF THE CHAIN!"
